mods.name: Jimk Free Crafting Module
mods.author: Jimk72
mods.description: A handy Workshop module(Under Jimk Innovations) that allows you to craft everything in Icarus for free. Adds New slot when Equipped!

mods.name: Jimk Higher Base Payouts For Missions
mods.author: Jimk72
mods.description: Bump All mission rewards up to 650 base for Ren and 600 base for Exotics if mission has exotic rewards! Licence up to 5 and Biomass up to 30.

mods.name: Jimk Kryptic Workshop Tent
mods.author: Jimk72
mods.description: Adds a Kryptic camo tent to the JimK Innovations tab in the workshop.

mods.name: Jimk Workshop Pets
mods.author: Jimk72
mods.description: Adds a Bear Cub, Raccoon, and Rabbit pets plus Moa and Actic Moa mounts and saddle, available in the workshop under the Jimk Innovations tab. Pets have similar talents as the cat. Max level is 25. V1.2 Updated rabbits AI. Rabbits are still in beta!

mods.name: Jimk Prometheus Map Full
mods.author: Jimk72
mods.description: Adds the missing Map image files for the Null zone in Prometheus.

mods.name: Jimk Upright Double Freezer
mods.author: Jimk72
mods.description: A Double Wide Upright Freezer. Consumes 3000 power and has 60 slots.

mods.name: Jimk Multi Teleport
mods.author: Jimk72
mods.description: Handheld device available from workshop tab Jimk Innovations. Allows the saving of 18 locations each for Olympus, Styx and Prometheous. Right mouse button allows you to name and save locations and left mouse button recalls those locations.

mods.name: Precision Bow Variants
mods.author: Jimk72
mods.description: A Desert and Forest Camo remake of my Precision Bow Designed by Dist7action. He did an amazing job on the new textures for these Bows! Both are crafted on the Fabricator.

mods.name: Jimk Kryptic Camo Kit
mods.author: Jimk72
mods.description: New set of Workshop Armor using custom meshes which is a combination of my 2 favorite armours, Backpack, and Precision Compound Bow. All three have Kryptic camo design. Available in the Workshop under JimK Innovations tab. Also Includes a Kryptic camo Recurve Bow craftable in the Forge/Foundry.

mods.name: Jimk Barn Buildables
mods.author: Jimk72
mods.description: Everything you need to build the Barn of your dreams! All Items are crafted on the Carpentry Bench. All new wood grain texture, roof pieces with soffet hangovers, red painted exterior, sliding barn doors, hay bales for animals to eat from, custom doors and shutters, matching fences and gate pieces, matching interior deployables, stable walls with metal bars. Ver. 1.2, Added several more roof/wall pieces, several beam options. Re did Lights. Should help with FPS

mods.name: Jimk Mass Storage
mods.author: Jimk72
mods.description: Workshop Item found under JimK Innovations tab. When consumed gives a 100 slot storage container and a remote for accessing it when ever you are on the Planet. Can also be accessed locally. Costs 1000 Ren and 650 Exotics to research and then 50 Ren and 50 Exotics to craft.

mods.name: Jimk Foundry Remake
mods.author: Jimk72
mods.description: Replaces the Foundry with a slightly smaller model with all the extra models removed so it fits in your base like all the rest of the benches. Also Reduced its weight to adjust for less equipment.

mods.name: Jimk Moa Upgrade
mods.author: Jimk72
mods.description: Upgrades Moa and Actic Moa Talents to be faster, more storage, better to defend and have more usage! Makes fully leveling up a Moa worth it! Does not effect the base stats!

mods.name: Jimk Precise Building Deployable
mods.author: Jimk72
mods.description: Rightclick when deploying building pieces to pop up a menu that allow precise placement of pieces in relation to other pieces. Makes it easy to do round building and custom floor.

mods.name: Jimk Larger Batteries
mods.author: Jimk72
mods.description: Adds two new Battery racks. A double and a Quad Rack. A little cheaper to craft as they have less metal combined. These are also stackable.

mods.name: Jimk Small Electrical wires
mods.author: Jimk72
mods.description: Shrinks down the electrical wire and nodes. Added Water Lines and Nodes.

mods.name: All Ammo Turret
mods.author: Jimk72
mods.description: Just for fun. Has custom turret model, fires full auto, shoots every type of ammo, arrows, and bolts. Goes through lots of ammo!

mods.name: Jimk Garden Planters
mods.author: Jimk72
mods.description: Adds several craftable planters to the game. Adds Craftable Exotic Planting Soil. This soil has 6 different versions that effect the plants differently. 1-Reduces plant size by 50% 2-Reduces plant size by 25% 3-Keeps standard plant size 4-Increases plant size by 150% 5-Increases plant size by 200% 6-Increases plant size by 400% The mutation prevents crops from being harvested so this is only for visual aesthetics! Fixed texture issues on concrete planters.

mods.name: Jimk Garden Deployables
mods.author: Jimk72
mods.description: Adds several Garden Deployables.

mods.name: Jimk Fences
mods.author: Jimk72
mods.description: A mod that adds several fences to the game and defensive razor wire. Has two types of wood fences each with a tall version for larger animals and chain link fencing for a more industrial look. Also includes matching gates for wood and chain link fences. Special thanks to Maxus! without his generous donation these would not be possible!

mods.name: Jimk Added Deployables
mods.author: Jimk72
mods.description: Ver 1.8 Updated for week 151, Removed Damage Modifiers. Contains Xtra Large Aquarium, Water Extractor, Vapor Collector, and Large Wind Turbine. All crafted on the Fabricator bench.

mods.name: Bear Mount
mods.author: Jimk72
mods.description: Allows the raising of cubs into full grown bear mounts. Bear now eats and drinks from deployables. Fully updated to use the new talents system for mounts. Created Custom Talent tree with Bear background image and center Icon. Still can only use the standard saddle and the cargo saddle.

mods.name: Battery Powered Storage
mods.author: Jimk72
mods.description: A workshop battery powered crate to keep your food fresh! Found under Jimk Innovations tab in workshop.

mods.name: Better Lights
mods.author: Jimk72
mods.description: Makes the flashlight, Torch, and Lantern bright to fill the darkness. Fixed for week 127 update.

mods.name: Better Pistol Turret
mods.author: Jimk72
mods.description: Increases fire rate, increases targeting rate and turret movement, increases inventory slots, increased durability, and reduced power requirements to 1000.

mods.name: Jimk Steel Buildables
mods.author: Jimk72
mods.description: Has reduced crafting costs for all items. Adds new steel building pieces crafted in the tier4 Forge. Contains Walls, Door, Double Door, Angled Wall, HalfPitches, Corner Pieces, Floors, Half Floors, Ramps, Frames, Stairs, Beams, Railings, Ladders, and a Bed. Strongest Building material in game.

mods.name: Building Height Strength
mods.author: Jimk72
mods.description: Changes all building materials to be stronger than concrete for super tall structures. Vers. 2.5 Added missing Building Types.

mods.name: Glass Buildables
mods.author: Jimk72
mods.description: Updated original glass pieces to use new glass and steel textures and added full new tier of glass building pieces. All craftable on the glass bench.

mods.name: Better Glass
mods.author: Jimk72
mods.description: Replaces Glass from original glass building pieces. Fixed issues with destructables loosing textures. Already included with Glass Buildables.

mods.name: Camera Distance
mods.author: Jimk72
mods.description: Allows the photo camera to move far away from player to get better shots.

mods.name: Clear Photo Lens
mods.author: Jimk72
mods.description: Removes Lens, frame, and text at bottom of screan for a clear view in photo mode.

mods.name: Concrete with Wood Interior
mods.author: Jimk72
mods.description: Gives more options when deploying concrete wall. Adds Interior wood option to the inside of concrete wall, door frame, window frame, double door frames. Adds option for short Interior wood beam, and Adds Iron reinforced interior wood floor. Crafted at the Machining Bench. Similar look as the reinforced door and with the strength of Stone floor. Ver 2.5 Added wall angles L,R,L Invert, R Invert, and Peak.

mods.name: Custom Puck Lights
mods.author: Jimk72
mods.description: Now Found in the Workshop under Jimk Innovations. Looks like a crate with Lights around it. Item that when consumed gives you a crate and 6 new types of deployable LED lights(No Power Needed). Including an Anti-Gravity light and Deployable Light switches to control them all with and various wall, floor, and ceiling lights.

mods.name: Custom Options Menu
mods.author: Jimk72
mods.description: Gives you a new menu when you right click with fists equiped. Includes custom jump heights, double jump, tripple jump, and adjusts out of bounds timer as well as clear vegitation and clear all storms. Can clear cave worms, server compatible now. Turn Lights On/Off, Fire sources, and Find corpses added. Now Pauses upon opening.

mods.name: Custom Options Handheld
mods.author: Jimk72
mods.description: Handheld that Gives you a new menu when you open it. Includes custom jump heights, double jump, tripple jump, and adjusts out of bounds timer as well as clear vegitation and clear all storms. Can clear cave worms, server compatible now. Turn Lights On/Off, Fire sources, and Find corpses added.

mods.name: Custom Options Laptop
mods.author: Jimk72
mods.description: Deployable Laptop available in the workshop under Jimk Innovations tab, that Gives you a Options menu when you open it. Includes custom jump heights, double jump, tripple jump, and adjusts out of bounds timer as well as clear vegitation and clear all storms. Can clear cave worms, server compatible now. Turn Lights On/Off, Fire sources, and Find corpses added.

mods.name: Elevators
mods.author: Jimk72
mods.description: A craftable platform that will raise character 1,2,3,4,8,or 16 floors. When Deploying hold R for different variations. Must be deployed on a floor structure. Updated to use my custom floor piece from my upcoming Steel Buildables mod.

mods.name: Extraction 10 Seconds
mods.author: Jimk72
mods.description: Changes the extraction speed to 10 seconds per ore. Updated to include all the new ores.

mods.name: Extraction 5 Seconds
mods.author: Jimk72
mods.description: Changes the extraction speed to 5 seconds per ore. Updated to include all the new ores.

mods.name: Faster Titanium
mods.author: Jimk72
mods.description: Increases Titanium in the world and speeds up processing for Titanium, Steel, and Aluminum.

mods.name: Halloween Pumpkins
mods.author: Jimk72
mods.description: Allows crafting of several variations of Halloween Pumpkins to deploy around your home.

mods.name: HK 417
mods.author: Jimk72
mods.description: HK_417 is a selectable semi and full auto rifle.

mods.name: HK 417 Camo
mods.author: Jimk72
mods.description: HK_417 is a selectable semi and full auto rifle.

mods.name: HK 417 Sienna
mods.author: Jimk72
mods.description: HK_417 is a selectable semi and full auto rifle.

mods.name: HK 417 Reflex
mods.author: Jimk72
mods.description: HK_417 Reflex is a selectable semi and full auto rifle with Reflex sight, Silencer, and Flashlight attached.

mods.name: Metal Cage
mods.author: Jimk72
mods.description: Allows the crafting of cage building materials for animals. Ver 1.3 Updated for week 117 changes. Ver 1.4 added to fabricator.

mods.name: CompoundBow Kryptic Camo
mods.author: Jimk72
mods.description: This is a replacement skin for the compound bow that matches my armor skin.

mods.name: Craftables
mods.author: Jimk72
mods.description: Allows crafting of large statues for display in your home or patio. Includes: Windmill(5000watts), wood cupboard, interior cupboard(Resized and snaps together), metal cupboard, Statues(Large Komodo,Large Buffalo, large caveworm, Superlarge caveworm, Deer stone, Deer wood, Elephant stone). Ver 2.5 Added snapping to all 3 cabinets.

mods.name: Durability
mods.author: Jimk72
mods.description: Bumps the durability to 120000 for almost all items.

mods.name: Easy Cave
mods.author: Jimk72
mods.description: Prevents worms from spawning and automaticly give your the Dehumidifier buff in all caves. Ver 1.2 added all new missions from the Great Hunts.

mods.name: Increase Stacks
mods.author: Jimk72
mods.description: 3.6 Added new Items from the Great Hunt. Increases all lower stacks to 100. Ver. 3.4 Added all new Items and increased refined wood, concrete mix, and Electronics to 1000.

mods.name: Increased Slots
mods.author: Jimk72
mods.description: There are several versions people have made this is mine that I use. It bumps up a few storage and firepits storage slots.

mods.author: Jimk72
mods.description: All Items over 5000 become 5000, all Items between 1000 and 5000 become 1000.

mods.name: Scoped rifle
mods.author: Jimk72
mods.description: Allows you to craft a scoped hunting rifle using the Fabricator bench. Has a 10x and 20x zoom option.

mods.name: Slider
mods.author: Jimk72
mods.description: This is similar to my Elevator mod but creates a platform that when standing on will slide out 4 or 8 floor spots in any direction. Updated with New floor model as original was modified by Devs so I decided to use a custom floor piece from my Steel Buildables mod that will be released soon.

mods.name: Teleporter
mods.author: Jimk72
mods.description: Now Added to Jimk Innovations tab! Is a workshop item that when consumed will give you a base station and a hand held controller. Once on the planet just place the teleporter base on any floor piece and when you want to return to the base just click the left mouse button when the handheld controller is equiped. You can add a second one that will be activalted by using the right mouse button. If there is an issue you can press the R key with handheld equipped to reset view.

mods.name: Weapons Pack 1
mods.author: Jimk72
mods.description: This gives you 2 new handguns, 2 assault rifles They are all tier 4 so require the Fabricator bench to craft.

mods.name: Weapons Pack 2
mods.author: Jimk72
mods.description: Fixed assault rifle with scope and sniper rifle that was originaly in game.require the Fabricator bench to craft.

mods.name: Workshop Armor Kryptic Camo
mods.author: Jimk72
mods.description: Replaces the workshop armor textures with custom ones that uses a green kryptic pattern.

mods.name: Jimk Innovations
mods.author: Jimk72
mods.description: Includes the following mods:Jimk Teleporter, Custom Puck Lights, Precision Bow Workshop, Battery Powered Storage,Workshop Pistols.

mods.name: Jimk Leveling Mod
mods.author: Jimk72
mods.description: Increases Display Level to 500, Max talents at level 200. Follows games default curve.

mods.name: Mini Fridge
mods.author: Jimk72
mods.description: Made by JimK72 & CK_Dexterhaven, an additional option for refrigeration - the stackable mini-fridge.

mods.name: Mini Generator
mods.author: Jimk72
mods.description: Replaces Biofuel generator models with a much smaller version so you can place it on top of items and allows them to be stacked.

mods.name: More Daylight
mods.author: Jimk72
mods.description: Its supposed to add more daylight hours to the game. Seems to work sometimes.

mods.name: No Poison Fish
mods.author: Jimk72
mods.description: Removes poisonous fish from all bodies of water.

mods.name: No Weather
mods.author: Jimk72
mods.description: Removes all weather from game. Updated for new DLC and new Storm Systems.

mods.name: Prefilled Items
mods.author: Jimk72
mods.description: When liquid and oxygen containers are crafted they will come pre filled.

mods.name: Paintings Fix
mods.author: Jimk72
mods.description: Fixes Paintings so they can be placed on other Deployables.

mods.name: Remove G Slot Restrictions
mods.author: Jimk72
mods.description: This mod allows you to place normaly G slot only items(Extractors, radars, ect) in any slot including character inventory. Really helps out the solo players!

mods.name: Thor Hammer
mods.author: Jimk72
mods.description: Allows Thors Hammer to be crafted on player for free. This hammer has been reduced in size so it is not visible on screen. This was done for creating videos so there is no hammer visible. Thors Hammer when equiped will allow you to Fly around(Left mouse button) and float in air(Right mouse button).

mods.name: Tier 3 Electricity
mods.author: Jimk72
mods.description: Moves the Biofuel generator and the spline tool to the Machining bench where it should be.

mods.name: Windmill Generator
mods.author: Jimk72
mods.description: Allows you to craft a windmill generator. Craftable in Machining/Fabricator Benches, Generates 5000watts. Updated for week 151! Ver 1.4 removed damage cycle!

mods.name: Zombie Wolf Texture
mods.author: Jimk72
mods.description: Changes the Wolfs texture to make it look like a zombie wolf.

mods.name: Precision Bow
mods.author: Jimk72
mods.description: Craftable bow on the fabricator bench with a custom precision bow with scope. Scope has built in range finder and auto adjusts based off ammo used. Must have unlocked the Compound Bow talent to be able to craft!

mods.name: Precision Bow Workshop
mods.author: Jimk72
mods.description: Workshop custom precision bow with scope. Located in the Workshop under the JimK Innovations tab. Scope has built in range finder and auto adjusts based off ammo used.

mods.name: Out Of Bounds Fix
mods.author: Jimk72
mods.description: Replaces Out of Bounds UI with small Notification and Auto Pauses around 5 seconds.

mods.name: Jimk Shotgun With Light
mods.author: Jimk72
mods.description: Adds A new Trench Shotgun with a Light attachment, increases ammo to 10 and has a slightly increased rate of fire.

mods.name: Scope For CrossBows
mods.author: Jimk72
mods.description: Adds scope UI when aiming to Titanium and Platinum Crossbow.
